OL,3,C#16 billion down? That's not entirely
OL,4,Ctrue Prime Minister
OL,6,FHe added: "There was no misleading,
OL,7,Fand I simply don't accept... that
OL,8,Fbeing told that the OBR productivity
OL,9,Freview means you've got #16 billion
OL,10,Fless than you would otherwise have had
OL,11,Fshows that you've got an easy starting
OL,12,Fpoint."
OL,14,FUnfortunately, this statement is a
OL,15,Fselective use of the OBR's analysis.
OL,16,FThe PM isn't inventing numbers; he's
OL,17,Fpresenting the bad news while ignoring
OL,18,Fthe good news the OBR handed him in a
OL,19,Fway that feels misleading.
OL,21,FHere's the full picture:
