OL,3,C#16 billion down? That's not entirely
OL,4,Ctrue Prime Minister
OL,6,FThe result? "Pre-measures" - that is
OL,7,Fto say, before the government had made
OL,8,Fany decisions - the PM was actually
OL,9,F"down" #5.7bn - not #16 billion.
OL,11,FAnd the Chancellor's buffer against
OL,12,Fher borrowing rule fell from #9.9
OL,13,Fbillion to #4.2 billion. She still met
OL,14,Fher main fiscal rule.
