OL,3,C#16 billion down? That's not entirely
OL,4,Ctrue Prime Minister
OL,6,FIn the run-up to the Budget, a series
OL,7,Fof stories - fed deliberately from
OL,8,Fwithin government - suggested that the
OL,9,Fweaker economic outlook had blown a
OL,10,Fhuge hole in the public finances. The
OL,11,FOBR's disclosures since the Budget
OL,12,Fshow that wasn't the case.
OL,14,FRachel Reeves knew this when she
OL,15,Fdelivered her extraordinary pre-Budget
OL,16,Fnews conference on November 4.
OL,18,FThe head of the OBR, Richard Hughes,
OL,19,Fwas concerned enough to write to the
OL,20,FTreasury Select Committee to "set out
OL,21,Fthe facts".
