OL,11,FAs the OBR documents show, taxes rose
OL,12,Fmainly to pay for welfare U-turns and
OL,13,Fto give the Chancellor a bigger
OL,14,Fcushion against her fiscal rules,
OL,15,Freassuring markets.
OL,17,FThe welfare cuts she had promised
OL,18,Fweren't delivered, and the previous
OL,19,Fheadroom she left against her fiscal
OL,20,Frules was too small to protect against
OL,21,Fshocks.
